OL,5,G0200 Casualty 24/7: Every Second Counts
OL,6,     FThe staff and patients of
OL,7,     FBarnsley's A&E department are put
OL,8,     Funder the microscope. 84-year-old
OL,9,     FTerry, comes in with a
OL,10,     Fbadly-broken ankle and fears he
OL,11,     Fmay never dance again.
OL,12,G0250 Skin A&E
OL,13,     FDr Toby Nelson checks a patient's
OL,14,     Fback and finds a pre-cancerous
OL,15,     Fmole, Dr Emma McMullen inspects a
OL,16,     Flipoma on a patient's buttock, and
OL,17,     FDr Dev Shah treats a collection of
OL,18,     Fskin tags.
